node.text:
Every year I look forward to the ODR it’s a place where memories are made that last a lifetime. It always passes too fast. I’m hoping those of you in colder climates were able to get out often and spend some quality time with family and friends. It’s time for me to put away the skates and join the #bladegang 
This clip is from our YT video where we rated every ODR within 30 minutes from our house. The people who volunteer to keep ODRs are amazing, including this friendly neighbour who volunteers his time and equipment to keep the rink perfect. He got stuck so the guys on the rink had to give him a push 😁 #canada #hockey

While watching hockey one day Olivia asked me "Where are the girl hockey players?" so I quickly put on some Women's Team Canada hockey highlights. Her face lit up and I could see she was filled with excitement and hope. We're excited to watch the Women's World Hockey Championship and in partnership with @telus invite you to enter to win the ultimate fan prize gift pack including: a signed Team Canada Jersey, a 55” Samsung 4K Smart TV, Sonos Soundbar, $200 gift card to SkiptheDishes, 1 year of SmartHome security + control with video.
 
I'm proud to be a #TELUS_Partner for all they do for hockey. They've recently donated $10k to the Hockey Nova Scotia Try-It Program to offer a chance for young girls to learn about hockey and get on the ice for the first time and regularly support local charities across Canada.

node.text:
Go Canada Go! This will be the first time our family will be watching the Summer Olympics, so it should be fun to see which sports the kids like the most. What is your family's favourite Olympic Summer sport to watch?

@Sobeys has made our family viewing party even better by sending over a Team Canada Viewing Kit full of snacks from Coca Cola, General Mills, Oreos, and more! Time to see what the kids enjoy more, the snacks or the games :D

Click the link in my bio to enter for your chance to win a Viewing Kit for your family!

Share your favourite snack while watching the Olympics and we might try it out! #SobeysPartner #Ad #FeedTheDream
